{"tid":2157190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐美自由陣營不滿美國對白俄人民的支持太低調 因美國想拉攏白俄總統盧卡申科遠離中俄","createTime":"2020-08-15T01:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T18:13:10.000Z","uid":100986,"like":5,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"70e394d41c8c092b8caa36ec66ae13a45b7f62f7","tid":2157190,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:09:28.000Z","msg":"歐美自由陣營不滿美國對白俄人民的支持太低調<br />\n<strong>因美國想拉攏白俄總統盧卡申科遠離支俄</strong><br />\n<br />\nThe U.S. Was Set to Send an Ambassador to Belarus. Then Came the Crackdown.<br />\nLawmakers threaten to block the confirmation of the first U.S. envoy to Belarus in over a decade. But others say an ambassador is needed now more than ever.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/08/12/belarus-lukashenko-elections-protests-united-states-diplomatic-relations/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2020%2F08%2F12%2Fbelarus-lukashenko-elections-protests-united-states-diplomatic-relations%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8ctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=b67ef9dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/08/12/belarus-lukashenko-elections-protests-united-states-diplomatic-relations/</a>"},{"pid":"f25a9598575606304d1d587d67825449dca3e796","tid":2157190,"uid":53687,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:10:30.000Z","msg":"管掂奶共德國先啦"},{"pid":"c3db17bc4b67b6528b6dfa85a90dfad07636a3c7","tid":2157190,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:16:22.000Z","msg":"Belarus, a highly authoritarian state, has been rocked by unprecedented protests since Sunday after highly dubious elections handed Lukashenko a sixth term. U.S. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo described the elections as &ldquo;not free and fair.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">But other congressional aides and diplomats said sending a U.S. envoy to Belarus is critical to both pushing back against the Lukashenko regime&rsquo;s abuses&mdash;and forestalling even more influence there from rivals like Russia and China. <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Keeping [Belarus] out of the Chinese orbit and helping them pull away from Russia, that&rsquo;s the bigger fight,&rdquo; said one Republican congressional aide. &ldquo;If you&rsquo;re going to have this fight, you&rsquo;re going to need to put a heavy hitter on the ground in Minsk.&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\nThe U.S. Was Set to Send an Ambassador to Belarus. Then Came the Crackdown.<br />\nLawmakers threaten to block the confirmation of the first U.S. envoy to Belarus in over a decade. But others say an ambassador is needed now more than ever.<br />\n<a href=\"https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/08/12/belarus-lukashenko-elections-protests-united-states-diplomatic-relations/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2020%2F08%2F12%2Fbelarus-lukashenko-elections-protests-united-states-diplomatic-relations%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8ctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=b67ef9dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/08/12/belarus-lukashenko-elections-protests-united-states-diplomatic-relations/</a>"},{"pid":"214d2c68ec16bd7d14aea146203d7b2246c8a0ca","tid":2157190,"uid":165113,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:22:10.000Z","msg":"好正常 有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e0d94a46dd64690cdcbf4d27375ead09dbcb8c","tid":2157190,"uid":47492,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:23:00.000Z","msg":"德國對支那咁奶又點計"},{"pid":"3c7ebd98473c4190e940798e5a57e2635afd5fdb","tid":2157190,"uid":8308,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:25:30.000Z","msg":"只有建立親美政權先有得改變<br />\n一日仲係中俄勢力範圍下 點支持人民都冇用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a313c84d1ae24aaabb8db5759fcba42a73a7cbd","tid":2157190,"uid":108269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":